Region:
UAE
Dubai
Post Date:
06/05/2014
Job Ref:
traffic manager
Job Description: Bored.com Ltd is a mixed media online entertainment portal, and we are looking for a Website Marketing and Traffic Manager to handle everything traffic related on our network of sites. It is essential for any candidates to show proven examples where they have used their own initiative to grow traffic on websites with no management or supervision. We are looking for someone who understands how to grow traffic using conventional AND non-conventional marketing methods. Responsibilities: Your key responsibility is to build our site through external marketing with both free and paid advertising quickly and at a profitable rate. To do this:
Daily analysis of traffic across the network of websites and creating presentable reports to discuss with other department heads; Managing all aspects of media buying campaigns including sourcing campaigns, producing creatives, and monitoring results; Supervising and managing social media presence - not just obvious things like Youtube channels and Facebook campaigns - you must be creative to build our brands; Coming up with creative strategies to distribute our content cost effectively Managing content distribution through small portals and small webmasters - e.g. game distribution; Helping to hire your subordinate staff and build your traffic/external marketing team
Requirements: - Proven track record of website traffic management (with examples);- Someone who can think outside the box;- Management experience is a plus - you may be expected to manage staff- Understanding of HTML5 and Photoshop;- Experience using Google Analytics and other traffic analysis tools;- Experience with Google Ads, DFP or similar;- 5 years + working in the Internet Biz;- Email marketing experience.
